      "description": "This COU applies exclusively to non-cannulated 7.5 mm titanium-alloy pedicle screw constructs tested under quasi-static (monotonic) compression-bending per ASTM F1717. Cannulated variants, dynamic fatigue loading, polyaxial screw heads, and screws with outer diameter outside 7.3–7.7 mm are explicitly excluded. Clinical spinal segment loading (in vivo) is outside scope; the model is not validated for in vivo predictions."
